CatDescriptText: A man working on electronics at a work table in an electronic repair shop.  Against the wall are devices used to test electric current.  Spare parts and broken electronics are on the equipment and work table.  On the wall is a sign, which states  "Not Responsible For Goods left Over 30 Days."
TitMainTitle: Man wearing light colored shirt with rolled up sleeves, seated at table repairing radios in shop with concrete block walls
